With innovation and entrepreneurship in our DNA, we are ready for the future of healthcare.

As one of the major healthcare groups in Latin America, we are making medicine more predictive and care personalised. We are pushing the boundaries of efficiency and user experience in the sector. Treating each patient as a whole person, in the centre of our attention. All that powered by the intelligent use of data.

Healthcare systems create enormous quantities of diverse, disconnected data. These often unstructured data have the potential to offer invaluable insights to improve people's lives, however they also present substantial analytic challenges.

Our Data Science and Artificial Intelligence practice has a team of brilliant people, all passionate about both healthcare and AI, passionate about solving problems. We like people who are smart, creative and highly motivated to deliver the best possible experience to our users. With high amounts of data, a highly qualified team, and a culture of learning, innovation and entrepreneurship, we believe you can have the best environment for your development.

We are currently looking for high-potential talents to perform as a Data Scientist.

Responsabilidades e atribuições

Working in teams, together with senior data scientists, data analytics specialists, designers and medical doctors, you will:

Analyse and pre-process data;
Generate insights and recommendations;
Design and implement quantitative solutions to problems, from presenting the right information to automating and optimizing decisions;
Develop machine learning and other quantitative models;
Develop reusable and well documented tools, adherent to high quality coding standards, and mathematically and statistically sound.

Requisitos e qualificações

Exceptional analytical, problem solving and quantitative skills;
Previous experience developing a project in Python. Proficiency in SQL;
Ability to learn fast and to find technical answers through research of existing knowledge;
Self-motivation;
Ability to deliver results through strong teamwork;
Desire to develop as a data scientist.

